== Early Life ==
Andrey Trotsky was born on October 31st, 1988 in Moscow. He was born because his father didn't pull out. His father Mikhail Trotsky (1953-2013) was a mail carrier, his mother Streltsova Valentinovna (1949-2016) was a flight attendant. In 1994 he was enrolled in primary school. In 1997 when he was 9 he started taking acting lessons. When he was 10 he fell in love and starting dating his girlfriend Ulyana Anatolievna (1988-2009) (more about this in Personal Life paragraph). In 2001 he made proposal and Ulyana agreed! In 2004 when he was 16 he made sex to Ulyana and year after she born triplets! Boys were named Igor, Alexey and Ilya. In 2005 he graduated from secondary school.

== Personal Life ==
