== Career ==
Andrei Trotsky has starred in various films and TV series since the age of 18, including famous and not so famous ones. His most famous role was in the series The Altos, where he played a supporting role in the third season, but unfortunately this series was closed immediately after the season with Andrey was released. His career was very short, and unfortunately I have almost nothing to say here, because he could have played even more roles but was prisoned and died early.

